Punishing the treacherous Captain
Captain Gort rebels! He threatens to kill the Elder and the Chosen to become the sole master of the village! You cannot allow that; the traitor and his accomplices must be destroyed!
#subobj  1
Find the Captain
The Captain escaped to gather the remaining brigands and attack the village. It is unlikely he managed to get too far; you'll probably find him in the Foothills near the road to the village.
#subobj  2
Kill the Captain
The traitor and his henchmen must be destroyed!
